name: Determine Combined Prefix
title: Determine Combined Prefix
notes:
**Note:** Combined Source of 1 or 2 indicate the Combined fields is based on the Clin field or Path field respectively.   
Combined Source of 3 indicates a combination of data was used to set the Combined value. For example, 4a and 4b were combined to derive 4c.  The prefix will be set to 'p'.  
Combined Source of 9 indicates the source is Unknown.  It should only occur if the value is 88.  No prefix will be set.
